treasuryAccount.description: Return account address of treasury. The account address can then be used to query the chain for balance

treasuryBalance.description: Return free balance of treasury account. In the context of PoA, only free balance makes sense for treasury. But just in case, to check all kinds of balance (locked, reserved, etc), get the account address with above call and query the chain.

getTotalEmissionInEpoch.description: Return total (validators + treasury) emission rewards for given epoch

tokenUsdPrice.description: Gets the price of Dock/USD from pallet's storage

tokenUsdPriceFromContract.description: Gets the price of Dock/USD from EVM contract

getCallFeeDock.description: Accepts a scale-encoded extrinsic, returns fee in DOCK as Balance (u64)

psPublicKeyWithParams.description: Return PS public key with params

psParamsByDid.description: Return all PS params by a DID

psPublicKeysByDid.description: Return all PS key with params by a DID

bbsPublicKeyWithParams.description: Return BBS public key with params

bbsParamsByDid.description: Return all BBS params by a DID

bbsPublicKeysByDid.description: Return all BBS key with params by a DID

bbsPlusPublicKeyWithParams.description: Return BBS+ public key with params

bbsPlusParamsByDid.description: Return all BBS+ params by a DID

bbsPlusPublicKeysByDid.description: Return all BBS+ key with params by a DID

accumulatorPublicKeyWithParams.description: Return Accumulator public key with params

accumulatorWithPublicKeyAndParams.description: Return Accumulator public key with params

didDetails.description: Get all keys, controllers and service endpoints of the DID

didListDetails.description: Get all keys, controllers and service endpoints of the DID
